                        <h5> <b>Welcome to www.mylistingtour.com, quick & easy virtual tour builder.</b></h5>
                        <p>
                            To begin building your virtual tour, login to your account.
                            If you are a new user, you can create an account/signup for free.
                            After login, you will be able to see your dashboard.
                            Dashboard has your profile picture, a buy now button, a create tour button, your account information and a list of your latest virtual tours.
                            You can edit your profile information by clicking on "Edit" button in the account information box.
                            You can buy new tours, by clicking on "Buy Tour" button below the profile picture. Payments are processed securely through PayPal. You can use credit card, debit card or PayPal account to make the payment.
                            Click on "Create Tour" button to start creating your virtual tour.
                        </p>
